Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode, how the goats were choosing a captain and a team name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The decision was made to race to the venue to determine the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When the goats were locked in a stalemate, they encountered Team Wolves reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After realizing the gap in their abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The goats learned to work together and arrived at the meeting place on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the tactics for dealing with the Team Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must remember
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our [number] match.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Only success is allowed, failure is not permitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you all have confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t be so tense, relax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, wait a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,During the previous match against the Team Rats
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the ball and wanted to break through the defense at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it failed, I was thinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could master that move…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it can help the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That move…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can master that move
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That would definitely be a great help to the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the ball always seems to lose its control when I accelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly am I lacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After this period of training
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve already developed a certain feel for dribbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re missing an opportunity right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This opportunity will come when it’s meant to; there’s no need to rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But tomorrow is our first match!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to practice more and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The opportunity will come naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to practice more and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The opportunity will come naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I still need to practice some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We absolutely cannot lose to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to work harder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then can we continue to play ball together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it still like this after practicing so many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who threw the ball around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With your short arms and legs, Goat Clan has absolutely no advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I play basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You’d better hurry home and do your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we absolutely cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Guardians’ journey has only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It can’t end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I must lead everyone to victory in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I now go for a run every night to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve become a starting player.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I’ve made the choice, I’m going to give it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is not just to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I also want to be the captain of the basketball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In order not to disappoint Wolnie and Wilie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to prove to everyone that I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you, I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you training too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m practicing breaking through defenses, but I just can’t seem to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you have a really great coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The coach simply said that the opportunity was lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But what exactly is this opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The coach didn’t tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Does “opportunity” refer to breaking through your own limitations during a critical moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve always been like this, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At a critical juncture
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have a match tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We absolutely cannot lose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As the future main basketball player of Team Wolves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m looking forward to a basketball showdown with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,good
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re so handsome! Can you teach me that move I just used?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that maybe we can win the game tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I’m tired of playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one teaches me, then I’ll learn on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve been playing basketball for so long and I still can’t master the moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Italy won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you teach me a powerful trick that guarantees victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no magic tricks in basketball that guarantee a win no matter what you learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But tomorrow is our team’s first official match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If we lose, my basketball team and my teammates’ games will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dream was shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need right now is not a magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Z
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, adjust your mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,mindset
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the game no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on the game and do your best in everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the strongest version of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do your best in everything you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what’s your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Help…help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m here to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie 00
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with the ball at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You come over here and hide for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Haste makes waste; don’t overthink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and the opportunity will come naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? How did you dodge in that instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I’ve mastered the feeling of breaking through at high speed without losing the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Squad leader, so you’re out training too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel I still haven’t practiced enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this help everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys go back and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still feel it’s not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, could you give us extra practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourselves, you have done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, trust your teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Basketball is a five-player sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t try to take everything on yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one night has passed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re like completely different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My mental state is much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need to do is enjoy the game and focus on the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best in everything you can
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s how we become the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s all cheer each other on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,come on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,come on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Set off
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi?
